MEDICAL ENTERPRISES, LLC, et al., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
The SURGERY & ENDOSCOPY CENTER, LLC, et al., Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-3703 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. November 14, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The parties' joint notice for dismissal filed October 10, 2018, is treated as a notice of voluntary dismissal and is granted. This appeal is dismissed.
